citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:00 on
04-NOV-19.
Owner was contacted by phone and she stated she was out of town and not able to return for the inspection.
